	•	Dominants: Neptune → Uranus → (then the rest become distant, often Sun-clustered)
	•	Near-Sun chorus: Mercury, Venus, Earth, Mars
	•	Culture seed: the Sun is a star-law, not a blazing ruler. Neptune becomes the single great actor: myths of exile, patience, faint signals, deep time.

